Game wise, you start off with a limited ability of determining
these things at Glevel 2.  As you progress in Glevel, you will
find out more information about them, and get better at judging
values of items.  Here is a short list of what will change.

Glevel 1-4:   Level comparison
Glevel 5-9:   Strength comparison
Glevel 10-14: Dexterity comparison
Glevel 15-19: Constitution comparison
Glevel 20+:   AC comparison

